<h2 class="sectionedit3"><a name="bitmap" id="bitmap">bitmap</a></h2>
<div class="level2">
<pre class="code">bitmap()</pre>

<p>
(Known as get_bitmap before 0.9c)
</p>

<p>
Returns the HUD <span class="curid"><a href="doku.php?id=main:modding_docs:lua:viewport#bitmap" class="wikilink1" title="main:modding_docs:lua:viewport">bitmap</a></span> of this viewport.
</p>

