<h2 class="sectionedit4"><a name="from_map" id="from_map">from_map</a></h2>
<div class="level2">

<p>
(available from version 0.9c)
</p>
<pre class="code">from_map(x, y)</pre>

<p>
Converts the map coordinates (x, y) to
coordinates relative to the viewport <span class="curid"><a href="doku.php?id=main:modding_docs:lua:viewport#bitmap" class="wikilink1" title="main:modding_docs:lua:viewport">bitmap</a></span> and returns them.
</p>

